title: All Deaths and Pneumonia/Influenza Deaths Weekly, USA by 122 U.S. cities, May 2nd to October 17, 2009
name: All Deaths and Pneumonia/Influenza Deaths Weekly, USA by 122 U.S. cities, May 2nd to October 17, 2009
description: This dataset from the CDC MMWR (Morbidity and Mortality Weekly Report) give deaths from all causes and deaths from Pneumonia and Influenza. Values of -1 represent no available data. The values are weekly from May 2nd to October 17 2009

author.source: Center for Disease Control and Prevention
